Subject: drm/i915/display: Skip state checker for AS SDP infoframe enable
Mime-version: 1.0
Content-type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-transfer-encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: faa5259b1ea0f6237c1b8ff24aa3ce4b6faa2890
